Detailed Description

TREX core extensions for europa.

This classe defines all the basic extensions of europa that provide the core functionalities for the europa reactor. And are used by T_REEX to implement synchronization and execution or for the nddl modeler to acces to information that resides on T-REX in the model. These extensions include :

  • DeliberationScope The filter that limits europa to plan only in the planning window of the reactor [current tick, current tick+latency+lookahed]
  • SynchronizationScope The filter used during suynchronization to limit the planning problem to only the current tick
  • CheckInternal A constraint that can be used to check if a europa object is a TREX Internal timeline
  • CheckExternal A constraint that can be used to check if a europa object is a TREX External timeline.
Author:
Frederic Py <fpy@mbari.org>
